# Local Terraform directories
**/.terraform/
.terraform.lock.hcl

# Terraform state files
**/terraform.tfstate
**/terraform.tfstate.backup

# Crash log generated by Terraform in case of a crash
**/crash.log

# Ignore override files as they are usually used to override resources and should not be shared
**/override.tf
**/override.tf.json
**/*_override.tf
**/*_override.tf.json

# Ignore generated plan files
**/*.tfplan

# Ignore .DS_Store files (common on macOS)
**/.DS_Store

# Ignore temporary files created by editors and IDEs
**/*.swp
**/*.bak
**/*.tmp
**/*~
